{
  "stem": "353.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was an underground movement in-- in Brinnlitz, and was five sets of five people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know about it that it's five sets, or 10 sets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We know only that the one set--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Separate set of five people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those were all part of Schindler's factory, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my unit were Joe [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH] was a Russian boy, [NON-ENGLISH] was a Russian boy-- born in Russia-- Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which means they went to army, and then later they were, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how you say, the Germans--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Captured and they didn't-- they didn't reveal their religion and they were kept in-- in [NON-ENGLISH] or [NON-ENGLISH], or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somehow, from Budzin they came to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from Majdanek they came to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], and Victor Lewis-- this was I-- we didn't know that existed another unit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew only about this one unit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now after the war, we got to know that Schindler knew about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is an underground movement but he said nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Talking about Schindler, I want to tell you he was a wonderful man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He, as far I understand now and read about him, and are reading about him and getting to know from other people-- because I didn't know him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I got to know him--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got to know about Schindler when to I moved to Brinnlitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was October 1944, and the end of the year was next May.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very short time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But people were talking, praising very, very high.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He, himself, was a rich man from Sudetenland, where we were, from the same town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was a spy for Hitler before 1939. 1937.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think somewhere before 30th.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] some people saying that he loves money.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
